                        <interp inst="t18800301-301-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>Collier was strongly recommended to mercy by the Jury on account of his age.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder.</hi>
